headline.print_headline: Obama to Act on Keystone in Next Couple of Months
headline.main: Obama to Act on Keystone in Next Couple of Months

lead_paragraph: President Barack Obama told governors at a White House meeting Monday that he expects to decide on the proposed Keystone XL oil pipeline from Canada in the next couple of months, two Republican governors said.
